227
00:25:03,260 --> 00:25:09,260
 It is set in Constantinople in 1204, around ten years after the date of the Prey manuscript.

228
00:25:09,260 --> 00:25:19,260
 And it mentions a Shroud of Christ displayed in some kind of ceremony in which the Shroud, with its figure of Christ, was raised up every Friday.

229
00:25:22,260 --> 00:25:45,260
