230
00:25:46,260 --> 00:25:50,260
 What does he mean by the image or the figure was lifted up?

231
00:25:50,260 --> 00:26:04,260
 A kind of rite or a special ritual happened every Friday in the Blacherne church, related to the demonstration of the Shroud of Christ.

232
00:26:04,260 --> 00:26:14,260
 It seems to me very probable that the Constantinopolitan Shroud and the Shroud of Turin is one and the same piece.

233
00:26:15,260 --> 00:26:27,260
 Because of very rare similarities, and this extremely important evidence by Robert de Clary, that there was an image of Christ on the Shroud.

234
00:26:27,260 --> 00:26:42,260
