00:37:33,260 --> 00:37:38,260
 Guskin believes all three blood features can be found on the Sudarium.

354
00:37:39,260 --> 00:37:46,260
 The first is the blood group, okay, which is a relatively rare blood group on the planet.

355
00:37:46,260 --> 00:37:51,260
 It's the blood group AB, okay, and it's the same blood group of human blood on both cloths.

356
00:37:51,260 --> 00:38:00,260
 Then there's also the differentiation between life blood, in other words, blood shed in life, and post-mortem blood, which can be clearly differentiated.

357
00:38:00,260 --> 00:38:03,260
 And again, that coincides on both cloths.

